			<div class="col-lg-12">
				<div class="question">
					<h4 class="title">What is Community Impact? </h4>
					<p class="answer">
					Community Impact is making meaningful changes to the community that needs attention, care and love.
					</p>
				</div>
				<hr />
				<div class="question">
					<h4 class="title">What is the goal?</h4>
					<p class="answer">
					The goal is to make a Change. Change happens when service oriented individuals from different backgrounds unite and work together to empower the struggling communities to thrive. We want to bring that change and we want to see smile in their faces. 
					</p>
				</div>
				<hr />
				<div class="question">
					<h4 class="title">What does the ABCO CI team do?</h4>
					<p class="answer">
					This is a volunteer team which provides time and effort for someone who is in need of help. 
					Some activities of ABCO IT team are but not limited to 
					<ul>
						<li>Support elderly and orphaned kids</li>
						<li>Tutoring in school (Quiz contest, Drawing competition)</li>
						<li>Beautify the environment (coastal cleanup, tree plantation)</li>
					</ul>
					</p>
				</div>
				<hr />
				<div class="question">
					<h4 class="title">How to Help ?</h4>
					<p class="answer">
					There are two ways you can help
					<ul>
						<li>Physically - Engage physically in the community Impact team activities during week days and in weekends.</li> 
						<li>Financially - you can make In-Kind donation for CI team activities.</li> 
					</ul>
					</p>
				</div>
				<hr />
				<div class="question">
					<h4 class="title">Who do I contact for Financial contribution ?</h4>
